**Quality Loop:** No

### Reasoning
- Title contains "Fix unused variable"

<!-- solve:phases=exec,qa -->
<!-- solve:skip-spec=true -->
<!-- solve:browser-test=false -->
<!-- solve:quality-loop=false -->`;

